These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, chess
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, dressmaker, nurse
House: art-deco, cape-cod, farmhouse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, mirinda
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person playing go is between the dressmaker and the nurse##2
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the farmhouse house is the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Game         | mah-jongg | go   | chess   |
| Job   | dressmaker     | security-guard | nurse |
| House   | farmhouse  | art-deco    | cape-cod      |
| Beverage     | coffee     | fanta      | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, scrabble
City: berlin, prague, colone
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, april, may
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, woodworking
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person traveling to prague and the person playing scrabble##2
6. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Game          | monopoly  | go     | scrabble     |
| City   | prague     | colone     | berlin      |
| Birthday   | may  | april | june |
| Hobby           | woodworking | magic-tricks     | drawing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, lavender, purple
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, country
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, bike, snowmobile
1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the fan country##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person who likes purple and the fan country##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bike is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person driving the roller is the fan gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage          | soy-milk  | iced-tea     | hot-chocolate     |
| Color           | purple | amber  | lavender   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | gospel    | country |
| Transport           | snowmobile     | roller | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, electronic, jazz
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, traveling, photography
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, september
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, crime
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the fan electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the fan jazz is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's birthday is in january##2
4. the fan electronic is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre    | blues       | jazz  | electronic   |
| Hobby     | traveling    | photography  | baking |
| Birthday     | october   | september | january        |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | comedy     | martial-arts      |

