The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, april
1. the spanish is on the left of the american##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is between the spanish and the siglo-smoker##2
3. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage          | lemonade    | milk     | soy-milk      |
| Cigar         | alhambra | davidoff | siglo |
| Nationality   | spanish  | american       | egyptian       |
| Birthday           | may     | september       | april     |

