.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, horse, chinchilla
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, security-guard, pilot
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, jazz, metal
City: marseilles, nizza, berlin
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan techno##1
2. the security-guard is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person traveling to marseilles##2
3. the fan jazz is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
5. the security-guard is between the pilot and the fan techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Pet          | chinchilla      | horse   | goat |
| Job         | dancer | security-guard | pilot |
| Music-Genre   | techno      | metal | jazz   |
| City     | berlin         | nizza  | marseilles       |

