.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, taxi
House: farmhouse, modern, art-deco
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, satire, epic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball, lacrosse
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person watching sports movies is between the modern house and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Transport      | jet-ski       | van      | taxi      |
| House         | modern    | art-deco | farmhouse      |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | sports     | satire |
| Sport   | volleyball     | lacrosse          | rugby       |

