.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, mauve, ivory
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, dancing, chess
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, june, october
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, montecristo
1. the montecristo-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the game-smoker##1
6. the game-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Color      | lilac      | mauve | ivory     |
| Hobby          | dancing   | skydiving      | chess     |
| Birthday   | october  | february      | june |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | montecristo        | game     |

