There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, water
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, apple, raspberry
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, argentine, american
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking fanta and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the person eating raspberry is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person eating apple is the person drinking water##1
5. the american is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the colombian is the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Cigar       | oliveros       | bongani       | dunhill    |
| Beverage         | water | almond-milk | fanta |
| Food       | apple      | raspberry         | cabbage |
| Nationality   | colombian        | american            | argentine  |

