The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, photographer, videographer
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, subway
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, zucchini, asparagus
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the photographer and the firefighter##2
5. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
6. the firefighter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Birthday      | march     | june | november      |
| Job         | photographer  | videographer       | firefighter |
| Transport   | subway   | bus         | quad-bike     |
| Food   | pomegranate | zucchini    | asparagus     |

