3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is between the fan indie and the person traveling to miami##2
6. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
