3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who growstulip is the person driving the tram##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Nationality      | egyptian    | french          | argentine |
| Flower          | daisy | marigold           | tulip        |
| Game           | go | backgammon | mah-jongg         |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | bus    | tram      |

