The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, lawyer, firefighter
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, orange, chestnut
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, water
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the firefighter is between the person drinking milk and the designer##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes orange is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday       | june | april | august |
| Job         | designer   | firefighter       | lawyer        |
| Color       | chestnut | azure   | orange         |
| Beverage   | water    | soy-milk     | milk         |

