City: london, hannover, liverpool
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, iris
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, tiparillo, siglo
1. the person traveling to hannover is between the siglo-smoker and the person traveling to london##2
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsiris is the person playing poker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Game   | billiard | poker  | canasta     |
| City   | liverpool    | hannover | london |
| Flower           | amaryllis        | iris   | zinnia  |
| Cigar     | siglo      | tiparillo   | chaman |

