.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, crime, disaster
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, april
There 3 different types of food: pear, papaya, mango
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, daffodil
1. the person who growsbellflower is the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person eating pear is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's birthday is in september##2
4. the person eating papaya is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person watching crime movies and the person eating papaya##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Movie-Genre      | musical | disaster     | crime        |
| Birthday         | may   | april | september |
| Food   | papaya        | pear       | mango      |
| Flower           | daffodil           | amaryllis    | bellflower       |

