.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, baking
City: venice, nizza, liverpool
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine, turkish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the argentine is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person drinking sprite and the argentine##2
6. the turkish is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby        | gardening      | board-games | baking |
| City         | nizza     | liverpool    | venice        |
| Nationality       | argentine | turkish   | pakistani   |
| Beverage   | 7up          | hot-chocolate     | sprite       |

 